Package com.paypal.android.sdk.payments

PayPal Mobile SDK for Android

See:
          Description

Class Summary
PaymentActivity Primary Activity for simple payments with the PayPal Android SDK.
PayPalAuthorization Resulting information from PayPalFuturePaymentActivity.
PayPalConfiguration Defines the configuration parameters for the SDK, via the EXTRA_PAYPAL_CONFIGURATION intent extra at service startup.
PayPalFuturePaymentActivity Primary Activity for getting user consent for PayPal Future Payments with the PayPal Android SDK.
PayPalPayment Describes the transaction.

This object describes the payment request, and should be submitted to the PaymentActivity via the PaymentActivity.EXTRA_PAYMENT intent extra.
PayPalPaymentDetails Optionally describes additional amount details for a PayPalPayment.

This object specifies the the breakdown of a payment amount, including item subtotal, shipping, and tax.
PayPalService Service responsible for communicating with PayPal's servers.

This service should be started shortly before your code interacts with the service, and stopped when the user is finished.
